<title>UK: London gold fixes barely firmer in quiet market.</title>
<headline>London gold fixes barely firmer in quiet market.</headline>
<text>
<p>GOLD - Fixed at $340.20 just five cents above AM level. Quiet and off low on short covering after support prevented further weakening. Narrow range seen.</p>
<p>SILVER - Up five cents at $4.77/$4.79 recovering previous day's losses. Seen capped at $4.80.</p>
<p>PLATINUM - Also regaining losses on short covering. $415.00/$420.00.</p>
<p>PALLADIUM - $200.00/$205.00, up $8.50.</p>
</text>
